welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Moosburg, Germany! This charming city is known for its rich history, beautiful architecture, and warm hospitality. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Moosburg has to offer during your stay."

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Franz Josef Strauss Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The secondary terminal at Franz Josef Strauss Airport, primarily serving Lufthansa and its partner airlines.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport, with a 24-hour time limit per device.
